{"tid":666132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加強監控？美國華裔公民iphone遭中國政府跨國鎖機！","createTime":"2018-05-15T15:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T03:10:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"39e561426954b6ca19843aa5ddeff49c655d13af","tid":666132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"jayng<br />\n<br />\n日前，住在美國休斯敦的美國華裔公民 Peter Wong 向當地蘋果客服投訴，指他的蘋果iphone在一夜間從正常運作變成一塊磚頭。可惜的是，蘋果客服回覆指，他的iphone是被中國方面鎖死了。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這名用戶在註冊蘋果帳號的時候，設定成中國帳號，在蘋果將中國 iCloud 服務交到雲上貴州營運後，似乎認為他的iphone中藏有敏感訊息而將其封鎖。現時他的蘋果 ID 及號碼均已被封鎖，當地蘋果客服對此亦無能為力。"},{"pid":"becce167c617e968e00bdee8f27f7680f63df956","tid":666132,"uid":113178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"勵害了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e7b4e3af1a24f0a742bb41bee9acaa8f502add","tid":666132,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.android-hk.com/news/china-apple-id-sec-android-hk-15518/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Fchina-apple-id-sec-android-hk-15518%2F&d=l%2BKlAbT4fi%2BxrQMUUF1vPDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3b2ff974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.android-hk.com/news/china-apple-id-sec-android-hk-15518/</a>"},{"pid":"1a2b5759332db91c15b100422d9f536495060cfb","tid":666132,"uid":37735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"安全<br />\n<br />\n雲上貴州真係安全啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264dec765e327e5540f2c18cb4117ba03b44cba7","tid":666132,"uid":89514,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58651d167c42656ee4abb2b57235113b393a2128","tid":666132,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"可